\newlabel{fig:checks}{{5}{13}{Mode-E acceptance checks (Stefan v4.6 brief~\S 10) as run in v4.6.3 for the candidate bundle. Seven of nine pass. Two remain pending: the pixel-correlation high-bar requires Lemma~E to be \emph {proven}, not conjectured (the candidate phases happen to align with Planck phases only structurally, not realisation-wise); the official Planck likelihood requires a coupled foreground/noise model that is outside Paper~7's scope}{figure.caption.5}{}}
